        <mxCell id="vt-conn-note" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;align=left;" value="On VIP failover — existing TCP connections are dropped and must reconnect&#xa;Clients reconnect to same VIP — no IP change — transparent to application config&#xa;All 3 VIPs are on the OT /27 subnet — [TBC: Brandon Hill to allocate]" vertex="1">
